high_descs: Turn right and face the brown square table in front of you.
Take the knife above the lettuce on top of the square table in front of you.
Turn around, then left, then right and face the microwave on your left.
Open the microwave, slice the apple inside and close the microwave again.
Turn right and face the microwave on your left.
Place the knife inside of the microwave in front of you and close it.
Turn left then face the microwave on your right.
Open the microwave in front of you, take out an apple slice and close the microwave.
Turn around and head towards the stove in front of you.
Place the apple slice in the pot on the stove in front of you.
Take the pot with the apple slice off the stove in front of you.
Turn right, then face the table with the toaster on it.
Place the pot on the table by the toaster in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a pot with an apple slice in it by the toaster.

high_descs: turn right, then move straight to the black table to the left of the counter top at the opposite end of the room
pick up the knife with the yellow handle from the table
turn around, make a left, and go face the microwave to the right of the trash can
open the microwave door and cut the potato in two pieces, then shut the door
face the microwave again after a few seconds of heating in the microwave
place the knife in the microwave with the potato
face the microwave again with the potato and knife in it after a few seconds
open the microwave door, remove a single slice in the microwave, and shut the door
walk directly across the room with the potato slice to the stove
place the potato slice in the pan with the handle
pick up the pan on the stove after a few seconds
turn right and go straight until you reach the table with the toaster
place the pan on the table to the right of the toaster
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato in the microwave to bring to the stove for further cooking

high_descs: turn right and walk to the black table at the end of the room to the left of the kitchen counter
grab the knife off of the black table
turn around and walk to the microwave in the corner of the room on the left
cup up the potato inside of the microwave
move to the right a bit so you are center with the microwave, then face the microwave
place the knife inside of the microwave
move to the left a bit and face the microwave again
grab the potato slice out of the microwave
turn around and walk to the stove at the end of the room
place the potato slice inside of the pan on the front right burner
grab the pan off of the burner
turn right and walk to the end of the kitchen table on your left
place the pan down on top of the kitchen table
anns.task_desc: place a pan with a potato slice in it down on the kitchen table

high_descs: Turn right and walk across the room to face the black table at the end of the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Walk to the opposite corner of the room to face the microwave.
Cut the potato in the microwave.
Step to the right and face toward the microwave.
Place the knife inside the microwave.
Take a step to the left and face the microwave.
Remove a slice of potato from the microwave.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the stove.
Place the potato slice into the pan on the back right burner.
Pick up the pan with the potato slice in it.
Step to the right to face the table to the left of the sink.
Place the pan with the potato on it on the table.
anns.task_desc: To cut a potato plus putting it in a pan as well as moving the pan from the stove to a table.

high_descs: Turn right, go forward to the black stand to the left of the sink counter.
Take the large knife on the left of the stand.
Turn around, go towards the wall, turn left before reaching the table, go forward and to the right to the microwave.
Cut the potato in the microwave into slices.
Stay at the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Stay at the microwave.
Take a slice of potato from the microwave.
Turn around, go to the oven across the room.
Put the slice of potato in the pot on the right front of the stove top.
Take the pot from the stove top.
Turn right, go forward to the black stand, turn right, go to the white table.
Put the pot on the white table to the right of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a slice of potato in it on a table.

high_descs: Walk in the direction of the stove, hang a right, walk to the brown table with the knife with a yellow handle on it.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle from the brown table.
Turn around and carry the knife to the microwave oven on the other side of the room.
Open the microwave oven door.
Slice the potato inside the microwave oven, close the door.
Open the microwave oven door, place the knife with the yellow handle behind the potato, with the blade facing to the left of the microwave oven, close the microwave oven door.
Open the microwave oven door.
Remove the center slice from the potato, close the microwave oven door.
Turn around and walk to the stove on the other side of the room.
Place the potato slice in the pan on the front right burner of the stove.
Pick up the pan using its handle.
Turn to your right and walk to the white table located to the right of the stove.
Place the pan with its handle pointing to the right on the right side of the white table and to the right of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Cook a potato, fry a potato slice, bring it to the white table
